               </div>
               <div style="padding: 24px;">
                  <div style="margin-bottom: 16px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.125rem; color: #111827;">Startup Requirements</div>
                  <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 0.875rem;">
                     <span style="color: #6b7280; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#ef4444" stroke-width="2"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"></line><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"></line></svg> Commercial Space</span>
